The provider type for the rancher2 package. By default, resources use package-wide configuration
settings, however an explicit `Provider` instance may be created and passed during resource
construction to achieve fine-grained programmatic control over provider settings. See the
[documentation](https://www.pulumi.com/docs/reference/programming-model/#providers) for more information.

        <span class="property-type">str</span>
    </dt>
    <dd>{{% md %}}Rancher connection timeout (retry every 5s). Golang duration format, ex: "60s"
{{% /md %}}</dd><dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">
        <span id="token_key_python">
<a href="#token_key_python" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;">token_<wbr>key</a>
</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">str</span>
    </dt>
    <dd>{{% md %}}API token used to authenticate with the rancher server
{{% /md %}}</dd></dl>
{{% /choosable %}}
